{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"It's Monday morning."},{"time":3000,"text":"In Washington,"},{"time":5000,"text":"the president of the United States"},{"time":7000,"text":"is sitting in the Oval Office,"},{"time":9000,"text":"assessing whether or not"},{"time":11000,"text":"to strike Al Qaeda"},{"time":13000,"text":"in Yemen."},{"time":15000,"text":"At Number 10 Downing Street,"},{"time":17000,"text":"David Cameron is trying to work out"},{"time":20000,"text":"whether to cut more public sector jobs"},{"time":23000,"text":"in order to stave off a double-dip recession."},{"time":26000,"text":"In Madrid, Maria Gonzalez"},{"time":29000,"text":"is standing at the door,"},{"time":31000,"text":"listening to her baby crying and crying,"},{"time":34000,"text":"trying to work out whether she should let it cry"},{"time":37000,"text":"until it falls asleep"},{"time":39000,"text":"or pick it up and hold it."},{"time":42000,"text":"And I am sitting by my father's bedside in hospital,"},{"time":46000,"text":"trying to work out"},{"time":48000,"text":"whether I should let him drink"},{"time":50000,"text":"the one-and-a-half-liter bottle of water"},{"time":53000,"text":"that his doctors just came in and said,"},{"time":56000,"text":"\"You must make him drink today,\" --"},{"time":58000,"text":"my father's been nil by mouth for a week --"},{"time":61000,"text":"or whether, by giving him this bottle,"},{"time":65000,"text":"I might actually kill him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68000,"text":"We face momentous decisions"},{"time":71000,"text":"with important consequences"},{"time":73000,"text":"throughout our lives,"},{"time":75000,"text":"and we have strategies for dealing with these decisions."},{"time":78000,"text":"We talk things over with our friends,"},{"time":81000,"text":"we scour the Internet,"},{"time":84000,"text":"we search through books."},{"time":87000,"text":"But still,"},{"time":89000,"text":"even in this age"},{"time":91000,"text":"of Google and TripAdvisor"},{"time":93000,"text":"and Amazon Recommends,"},{"time":96000,"text":"it's still experts"},{"time":98000,"text":"that we rely upon most --"},{"time":101000,"text":"especially when the stakes are high"},{"time":103000,"text":"and the decision really matters."},{"time":106000,"text":"Because in a world of data deluge"},{"time":108000,"text":"and extreme complexity,"},{"time":111000,"text":"we believe that experts"},{"time":113000,"text":"are more able to process information than we can --"},{"time":116000,"text":"that they are able to come to better conclusions"},{"time":119000,"text":"than we could come to on our own."},{"time":122000,"text":"And in an age"},{"time":124000,"text":"that is sometimes nowadays frightening"},{"time":127000,"text":"or confusing,"},{"time":129000,"text":"we feel reassured"},{"time":131000,"text":"by the almost parental-like authority"},{"time":134000,"text":"of experts"},{"time":136000,"text":"who tell us so clearly what it is"},{"time":139000,"text":"we can and cannot do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143000,"text":"But I believe"},{"time":145000,"text":"that this is a big problem,"},{"time":147000,"text":"a problem with potentially dangerous consequences"},{"time":151000,"text":"for us as a society,"},{"time":154000,"text":"as a culture"},{"time":156000,"text":"and as individuals."},{"time":158000,"text":"It's not that experts"},{"time":160000,"text":"have not massively contributed to the world --"},{"time":162000,"text":"of course they have."},{"time":164000,"text":"The problem lies with us:"},{"time":167000,"text":"we've become addicted to experts."},{"time":170000,"text":"We've become addicted to their certainty,"},{"time":173000,"text":"their assuredness,"},{"time":175000,"text":"their definitiveness,"},{"time":177000,"text":"and in the process,"},{"time":179000,"text":"we have ceded our responsibility,"},{"time":181000,"text":"substituting our intellect"},{"time":183000,"text":"and our intelligence"},{"time":186000,"text":"for their supposed words of wisdom."},{"time":189000,"text":"We've surrendered our power,"},{"time":192000,"text":"trading off our discomfort"},{"time":194000,"text":"with uncertainty"},{"time":196000,"text":"for the illusion of certainty"},{"time":198000,"text":"that they provide."},{"time":201000,"text":"This is no exaggeration."},{"time":204000,"text":"In a recent experiment,"},{"time":206000,"text":"a group of adults"},{"time":208000,"text":"had their brains scanned in an MRI machine"},{"time":211000,"text":"as they were listening to experts speak."},{"time":215000,"text":"The results were quite extraordinary."},{"time":218000,"text":"As they listened to the experts' voices,"},{"time":221000,"text":"the independent decision-making parts of their brains"},{"time":226000,"text":"switched off."},{"time":228000,"text":"It literally flat-lined."},{"time":231000,"text":"And they listened to whatever the experts said"},{"time":233000,"text":"and took their advice, however right or wrong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237000,"text":"But experts do get things wrong."},{"time":241000,"text":"Did you know that studies show"},{"time":244000,"text":"that doctors misdiagnose"},{"time":247000,"text":"four times out of 10?"},{"time":250000,"text":"Did you know"},{"time":252000,"text":"that if you file your tax returns yourself,"},{"time":255000,"text":"you're statistically more likely"},{"time":257000,"text":"to be filing them correctly"},{"time":259000,"text":"than if you get a tax adviser"},{"time":261000,"text":"to do it for you?"},{"time":263000,"text":"And then there's, of course, the example"},{"time":265000,"text":"that we're all too aware of:"},{"time":267000,"text":"financial experts"},{"time":269000,"text":"getting it so wrong"},{"time":271000,"text":"that we're living through the worst recession"},{"time":273000,"text":"since the 1930s."},{"time":277000,"text":"For the sake of our health,"},{"time":279000,"text":"our wealth"},{"time":281000,"text":"and our collective security,"},{"time":283000,"text":"it's imperative that we keep"},{"time":286000,"text":"the independent decision-making parts of our brains"},{"time":290000,"text":"switched on."},{"time":292000,"text":"And I'm saying this as an economist"},{"time":294000,"text":"who, over the past few years,"},{"time":296000,"text":"has focused my research"},{"time":298000,"text":"on what it is we think"},{"time":300000,"text":"and who it is we trust and why,"},{"time":303000,"text":"but also --"},{"time":305000,"text":"and I'm aware of the irony here --"},{"time":307000,"text":"as an expert myself,"},{"time":310000,"text":"as a professor,"},{"time":312000,"text":"as somebody who advises prime ministers,"},{"time":315000,"text":"heads of big companies,"},{"time":317000,"text":"international organizations,"},{"time":319000,"text":"but an expert who believes"},{"time":321000,"text":"that the role of experts needs to change,"},{"time":324000,"text":"that we need to become more open-minded,"},{"time":327000,"text":"more democratic"},{"time":329000,"text":"and be more open"},{"time":331000,"text":"to people rebelling against"},{"time":333000,"text":"our points of view."},{"time":336000,"text":"So in order to help you understand"},{"time":339000,"text":"where I'm coming from,"},{"time":341000,"text":"let me bring you into my world,"},{"time":344000,"text":"the world of experts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":346000,"text":"Now there are, of course, exceptions,"},{"time":350000,"text":"wonderful, civilization-enhancing exceptions."},{"time":356000,"text":"But what my research has shown me"},{"time":359000,"text":"is that experts tend on the whole"},{"time":362000,"text":"to form very rigid camps,"},{"time":365000,"text":"that within these camps,"},{"time":367000,"text":"a dominant perspective emerges"},{"time":370000,"text":"that often silences opposition,"},{"time":373000,"text":"that experts move with the prevailing winds,"},{"time":376000,"text":"often hero-worshipping"},{"time":379000,"text":"their own gurus."},{"time":381000,"text":"Alan Greenspan's proclamations"},{"time":383000,"text":"that the years of economic growth"},{"time":386000,"text":"would go on and on,"},{"time":389000,"text":"not challenged by his peers,"},{"time":392000,"text":"until after the crisis, of course."},{"time":396000,"text":"You see,"},{"time":399000,"text":"we also learn"},{"time":401000,"text":"that experts are located,"},{"time":403000,"text":"are governed,"},{"time":405000,"text":"by the social and cultural norms"},{"time":408000,"text":"of their times --"},{"time":410000,"text":"whether it be the doctors"},{"time":412000,"text":"in Victorian England, say,"},{"time":414000,"text":"who sent women to asylums"},{"time":417000,"text":"for expressing sexual desire,"},{"time":420000,"text":"or the psychiatrists in the United States"},{"time":423000,"text":"who, up until 1973,"},{"time":426000,"text":"were still categorizing homosexuality"},{"time":430000,"text":"as a mental illness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":432000,"text":"And what all this means"},{"time":434000,"text":"is that paradigms"},{"time":436000,"text":"take far too long to shift,"},{"time":439000,"text":"that complexity and nuance are ignored"},{"time":443000,"text":"and also that money talks --"},{"time":446000,"text":"because we've all seen the evidence"},{"time":449000,"text":"of pharmaceutical companies"},{"time":451000,"text":"funding studies of drugs"},{"time":454000,"text":"that conveniently leave out"},{"time":456000,"text":"their worst side effects,"},{"time":459000,"text":"or studies funded by food companies"},{"time":462000,"text":"of their new products,"},{"time":465000,"text":"massively exaggerating the health benefits"},{"time":468000,"text":"of the products they're about to bring by market."},{"time":471000,"text":"The study showed that food companies exaggerated"},{"time":473000,"text":"typically seven times more"},{"time":476000,"text":"than an independent study."}]},{"cues":[{"time":480000,"text":"And we've also got to be aware"},{"time":482000,"text":"that experts, of course,"},{"time":484000,"text":"also make mistakes."},{"time":486000,"text":"They make mistakes every single day --"},{"time":489000,"text":"mistakes born out of carelessness."},{"time":492000,"text":"A recent study in the Archives of Surgery"},{"time":495000,"text":"reported surgeons"},{"time":497000,"text":"removing healthy ovaries,"},{"time":500000,"text":"operating on the wrong side of the brain,"},{"time":503000,"text":"carrying out procedures on the wrong hand,"},{"time":506000,"text":"elbow, eye, foot,"},{"time":509000,"text":"and also mistakes born out of thinking errors."},{"time":512000,"text":"A common thinking error"},{"time":514000,"text":"of radiologists, for example --"},{"time":517000,"text":"when they look at CT scans --"},{"time":520000,"text":"is that they're overly influenced"},{"time":522000,"text":"by whatever it is"},{"time":524000,"text":"that the referring physician has said"},{"time":526000,"text":"that he suspects"},{"time":528000,"text":"the patient's problem to be."},{"time":531000,"text":"So if a radiologist"},{"time":533000,"text":"is looking at the scan"},{"time":535000,"text":"of a patient with suspected pneumonia, say,"},{"time":538000,"text":"what happens is that,"},{"time":540000,"text":"if they see evidence"},{"time":542000,"text":"of pneumonia on the scan,"},{"time":545000,"text":"they literally stop looking at it --"},{"time":548000,"text":"thereby missing the tumor"},{"time":550000,"text":"sitting three inches below"},{"time":552000,"text":"on the patient's lungs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":556000,"text":"I've shared with you so far"},{"time":559000,"text":"some insights into the world of experts."},{"time":562000,"text":"These are, of course,"},{"time":564000,"text":"not the only insights I could share,"},{"time":566000,"text":"but I hope they give you a clear sense at least"},{"time":569000,"text":"of why we need to stop kowtowing to them,"},{"time":572000,"text":"why we need to rebel"},{"time":574000,"text":"and why we need to switch"},{"time":576000,"text":"our independent decision-making capabilities on."},{"time":580000,"text":"But how can we do this?"},{"time":583000,"text":"Well for the sake of time,"},{"time":586000,"text":"I want to focus on just three strategies."},{"time":591000,"text":"First, we've got to be ready and willing"},{"time":593000,"text":"to take experts on"},{"time":596000,"text":"and dispense with this notion of them"},{"time":599000,"text":"as modern-day apostles."},{"time":601000,"text":"This doesn't mean having to get a Ph.D."},{"time":604000,"text":"in every single subject,"},{"time":606000,"text":"you'll be relieved to hear."},{"time":608000,"text":"But it does mean persisting"},{"time":611000,"text":"in the face of their inevitable annoyance"},{"time":614000,"text":"when, for example,"},{"time":616000,"text":"we want them to explain things to us"},{"time":618000,"text":"in language that we can actually understand."},{"time":623000,"text":"Why was it that, when I had an operation,"},{"time":626000,"text":"my doctor said to me,"},{"time":628000,"text":"\"Beware, Ms. Hertz,"},{"time":630000,"text":"of hyperpyrexia,\""},{"time":632000,"text":"when he could have just as easily said,"},{"time":634000,"text":"\"Watch out for a high fever.\""},{"time":638000,"text":"You see, being ready to take experts on"},{"time":642000,"text":"is about also being willing"},{"time":644000,"text":"to dig behind their graphs,"},{"time":647000,"text":"their equations, their forecasts,"},{"time":649000,"text":"their prophecies,"},{"time":651000,"text":"and being armed with the questions to do that --"},{"time":654000,"text":"questions like:"},{"time":656000,"text":"What are the assumptions that underpin this?"},{"time":659000,"text":"What is the evidence upon which this is based?"},{"time":662000,"text":"What has your investigation focused on?"},{"time":666000,"text":"And what has it ignored?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":669000,"text":"It recently came out"},{"time":671000,"text":"that experts trialing drugs"},{"time":674000,"text":"before they come to market"},{"time":676000,"text":"typically trial drugs"},{"time":679000,"text":"first, primarily on male animals"},{"time":683000,"text":"and then, primarily on men."},{"time":686000,"text":"It seems that they've somehow overlooked the fact"},{"time":689000,"text":"that over half the world's population are women."},{"time":694000,"text":"And women have drawn the short medical straw"},{"time":697000,"text":"because it now turns out that many of these drugs"},{"time":700000,"text":"don't work nearly as well on women"},{"time":703000,"text":"as they do on men --"},{"time":705000,"text":"and the drugs that do work well work so well"},{"time":708000,"text":"that they're actively harmful for women to take."},{"time":711000,"text":"Being a rebel is about recognizing"},{"time":714000,"text":"that experts' assumptions"},{"time":717000,"text":"and their methodologies"},{"time":719000,"text":"can easily be flawed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":722000,"text":"Second,"},{"time":724000,"text":"we need to create the space"},{"time":727000,"text":"for what I call \"managed dissent.\""},{"time":730000,"text":"If we are to shift paradigms,"},{"time":732000,"text":"if we are to make breakthroughs,"},{"time":734000,"text":"if we are to destroy myths,"},{"time":737000,"text":"we need to create an environment"},{"time":739000,"text":"in which expert ideas are battling it out,"},{"time":742000,"text":"in which we're bringing in"},{"time":744000,"text":"new, diverse, discordant, heretical views"},{"time":747000,"text":"into the discussion,"},{"time":749000,"text":"fearlessly,"},{"time":751000,"text":"in the knowledge that progress comes about,"},{"time":754000,"text":"not only from the creation of ideas,"},{"time":758000,"text":"but also from their destruction --"},{"time":761000,"text":"and also from the knowledge"},{"time":764000,"text":"that, by surrounding ourselves"},{"time":766000,"text":"by divergent, discordant,"},{"time":769000,"text":"heretical views."},{"time":771000,"text":"All the research now shows us"},{"time":773000,"text":"that this actually makes us smarter."},{"time":778000,"text":"Encouraging dissent is a rebellious notion"},{"time":781000,"text":"because it goes against our very instincts,"},{"time":784000,"text":"which are to surround ourselves"},{"time":787000,"text":"with opinions and advice"},{"time":789000,"text":"that we already believe"},{"time":792000,"text":"or want to be true."},{"time":794000,"text":"And that's why I talk about the need"},{"time":796000,"text":"to actively manage dissent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":800000,"text":"Google CEO Eric Schmidt"},{"time":802000,"text":"is a practical practitioner"},{"time":805000,"text":"of this philosophy."},{"time":807000,"text":"In meetings, he looks out for the person in the room --"},{"time":810000,"text":"arms crossed, looking a bit bemused --"},{"time":813000,"text":"and draws them into the discussion,"},{"time":816000,"text":"trying to see if they indeed are"},{"time":819000,"text":"the person with a different opinion,"},{"time":822000,"text":"so that they have dissent within the room."},{"time":825000,"text":"Managing dissent"},{"time":827000,"text":"is about recognizing the value"},{"time":830000,"text":"of disagreement, discord"},{"time":833000,"text":"and difference."},{"time":835000,"text":"But we need to go even further."},{"time":838000,"text":"We need to fundamentally redefine"},{"time":841000,"text":"who it is that experts are."},{"time":845000,"text":"The conventional notion"},{"time":847000,"text":"is that experts are people"},{"time":850000,"text":"with advanced degrees,"},{"time":852000,"text":"fancy titles, diplomas,"},{"time":855000,"text":"best-selling books --"},{"time":857000,"text":"high-status individuals."},{"time":859000,"text":"But just imagine"},{"time":861000,"text":"if we were to junk"},{"time":863000,"text":"this notion of expertise"},{"time":867000,"text":"as some sort of elite cadre"},{"time":871000,"text":"and instead embrace the notion"},{"time":874000,"text":"of democratized expertise --"},{"time":877000,"text":"whereby expertise was not just the preserve"},{"time":880000,"text":"of surgeons and CEO's,"},{"time":882000,"text":"but also shop-girls -- yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":886000,"text":"Best Buy,"},{"time":888000,"text":"the consumer electronics company,"},{"time":890000,"text":"gets all its employees --"},{"time":893000,"text":"the cleaners, the shop assistants,"},{"time":895000,"text":"the people in the back office,"},{"time":898000,"text":"not just its forecasting team --"},{"time":900000,"text":"to place bets, yes bets,"},{"time":903000,"text":"on things like whether or not"},{"time":905000,"text":"a product is going to sell well before Christmas,"},{"time":908000,"text":"on whether customers' new ideas"},{"time":911000,"text":"are going to be or should be taken on by the company,"},{"time":915000,"text":"on whether a project"},{"time":917000,"text":"will come in on time."},{"time":919000,"text":"By leveraging"},{"time":921000,"text":"and by embracing"},{"time":923000,"text":"the expertise within the company,"},{"time":925000,"text":"Best Buy was able to discover, for example,"},{"time":928000,"text":"that the store that it was going to open in China --"},{"time":932000,"text":"its big, grand store --"},{"time":934000,"text":"was not going to open on time."},{"time":937000,"text":"Because when it asked its staff,"},{"time":939000,"text":"all its staff, to place their bets"},{"time":942000,"text":"on whether they thought the store would open on time or not,"},{"time":946000,"text":"a group from the finance department"},{"time":949000,"text":"placed all their chips"},{"time":951000,"text":"on that not happening."},{"time":954000,"text":"It turned out that they were aware,"},{"time":956000,"text":"as no one else within the company was,"},{"time":959000,"text":"of a technological blip"},{"time":961000,"text":"that neither the forecasting experts,"},{"time":963000,"text":"nor the experts on the ground in China,"},{"time":966000,"text":"were even aware of."}]},{"cues":[{"time":970000,"text":"The strategies"},{"time":972000,"text":"that I have discussed this evening --"},{"time":975000,"text":"embracing dissent,"},{"time":977000,"text":"taking experts on,"},{"time":979000,"text":"democratizing expertise,"},{"time":981000,"text":"rebellious strategies --"},{"time":984000,"text":"are strategies that I think"},{"time":986000,"text":"would serve us all well to embrace"},{"time":988000,"text":"as we try to deal with the challenges"},{"time":991000,"text":"of these very confusing, complex,"},{"time":994000,"text":"difficult times."},{"time":996000,"text":"For if we keep"},{"time":998000,"text":"our independent decision-making part"},{"time":1000000,"text":"of our brains switched on,"},{"time":1003000,"text":"if we challenge experts, if we're skeptical,"},{"time":1006000,"text":"if we devolve authority,"},{"time":1008000,"text":"if we are rebellious,"},{"time":1010000,"text":"but also"},{"time":1012000,"text":"if we become much more comfortable"},{"time":1014000,"text":"with nuance,"},{"time":1016000,"text":"uncertainty and doubt,"},{"time":1019000,"text":"and if we allow our experts"},{"time":1022000,"text":"to express themselves"},{"time":1024000,"text":"using those terms too,"},{"time":1026000,"text":"we will set ourselves up"},{"time":1028000,"text":"much better"},{"time":1030000,"text":"for the challenges of the 21st century."},{"time":1034000,"text":"For now, more than ever,"},{"time":1037000,"text":"is not the time"},{"time":1039000,"text":"to be blindly following,"},{"time":1041000,"text":"blindly accepting,"},{"time":1043000,"text":"blindly trusting."},{"time":1046000,"text":"Now is the time to face the world"},{"time":1049000,"text":"with eyes wide open --"},{"time":1052000,"text":"yes, using experts"},{"time":1054000,"text":"to help us figure things out, for sure --"},{"time":1057000,"text":"I don't want to completely do myself out of a job here --"},{"time":1061000,"text":"but being aware"},{"time":1063000,"text":"of their limitations"},{"time":1066000,"text":"and, of course, also our own."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1070000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1072000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}